**Improvement Intent:** The performance issue identifies that `zipWithIndex` creates tuple allocations in hot paths. We will eliminate these allocations by replacing `zipWithIndex` with manual index tracking, using mutable local variables for iteration indices instead of generating tuple objects. This reduces GC pressure and improves throughput.

